<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_299" id="148v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_299_r1l19">Der Stat cʒu <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_299_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns iſt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>hren</expan> ~ dem Bẏſſchoff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_299_r1l21">von Paſſaw Als nehſtein ein brief kumen des vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_299_r1l22"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit ein abſchrifft ſchicken hyrynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_299_r1l23">daʒ ſich ewr vveiſheit auch darnach vviſʒ ʒu rihten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_299_r1l24"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ poſt kyliani </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_299_r1l25">VVinſheim <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_299" id="148v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>hren</expan> dem bysschoff von Passaw als nehstein ein brief kumen,
                        des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit ein abschrifft schicken
                        hyrynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>, daz sich ewr weisheit auch
                        darnach wisz zu rihten. <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v post Kyliani.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Winsheim <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
